            <title>[KAFKA-12754] TaskMetadata endOffsets does not update when the offsets are read</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-12754</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The high water mark in StreamTask is not updated optimally. Also it would be good to have the metadata offsets have a initial value of -1 instead of an empty map that way the set of TopicPartitions won&apos;t change.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
